1
00:02:14,428 --> 00:02:15,637
Hey, darling.

2
00:02:27,399 --> 00:02:29,443
Morning, Maeve.

3
00:02:30,068 --> 00:02:32,237
Late night talking or fucking?

4
00:02:32,821 --> 00:02:34,740
You're only getting paid for the latter.

5
00:02:35,240 --> 00:02:38,327
I get paid when they're grateful.

6
00:02:39,286 --> 00:02:41,246
Ain't always about
what's between my legs.

7
00:02:50,088 --> 00:02:51,131
<i>What are you looking at?</i>

8
00:02:51,798 --> 00:02:52,841
Don't shoot.

9
00:02:55,761 --> 00:02:56,803
<i>Newcomer.</i>

10
00:02:58,096 --> 00:02:59,639
Looks like a rough one.

11
00:02:59,806 --> 00:03:00,974
Give me a bottle.

12
00:03:02,517 --> 00:03:05,771
You're gonna need most of that
just to scrub the filth off him.

13
00:03:09,858 --> 00:03:12,110
Go find a mirror,
finish putting your face on.

14
00:03:13,487 --> 00:03:14,946
I'll handle this one.

15
00:03:37,511 --> 00:03:39,071
Aren't you gonna take your clothes off?

16
00:03:39,137 --> 00:03:41,497
I would, darling, but by the
time I got down to my knickers,

17
00:03:41,640 --> 00:03:43,141
I suspect you'd be done anyway.

18
00:03:47,479 --> 00:03:48,814
That's the spirit.

19
00:03:50,148 --> 00:03:53,026
Such a big man. So big all over.

20
00:03:53,318 --> 00:03:54,486
Except where it counts.

21
