something in return.

23
00:04:05,497 --> 00:04:06,665
Anything.

24
00:04:14,089 --> 00:04:15,340
That's it.

25
00:04:17,175 --> 00:04:18,260
Don't be shy.

26
00:04:37,863 --> 00:04:40,574
Oh, shit.

27
00:04:47,914 --> 00:04:50,792
Now then, where were we?

28
00:04:54,880 --> 00:04:57,066
- Did you show this to anyone?
<i>- Who would I show it to?</i>

29
00:04:57,090 --> 00:04:59,384
This wasn't some guest
with a Swiss Army knife.

30
00:04:59,551 --> 00:05:01,720
This was done by someone down here.

31
00:05:03,930 --> 00:05:05,724
<i>It did occur to me that it might be you.</i>

32
00:05:05,891 --> 00:05:07,577
But then I remembered
that you've been here forever.

33
00:05:07,601 --> 00:05:10,246
And if you were gonna sell us out,
you would have done that years ago.

34
