That look like anything to you?

72
00:10:51,861 --> 00:10:55,240
Not much to say.
The maze is an old Native myth.

73
00:10:56,282 --> 00:10:57,826
Regale me, Theodore.

74
00:10:59,661 --> 00:11:02,622
The maze itself
is the sum of a man's life,

75
00:11:02,789 --> 00:11:06,459
