76
00:11:06,751 --> 00:11:08,670
And there at the center,
there's a legendary man

77
00:11:08,837 --> 00:11:11,673
who'd been killed over and over again,
countless times,

78
00:11:11,840 --> 00:11:13,800
<i>but always clawed his way back to life.</i>

79
00:11:14,217 --> 00:11:15,577
<i>The man returned for the last time</i>

80
00:11:15,677 --> 00:11:18,763
