I was born. You were made.

112
00:13:26,015 --> 00:13:27,642
We feel the same.

113
00:13:28,226 --> 00:13:31,980
We are the same these days.
For the most part.

114
00:13:34,816 --> 00:13:36,401
One big difference, though.

115
00:13:38,820 --> 00:13:42,740
The processing power in here
is way beyond what we have.

116
00:13:43,491 --> 00:13:46,452
- It's got one drawback, though.
- What's that?

117
00:13:47,245 --> 00:13:48,579
You're under our control.

118
00:13:49,956 --> 00:13:52,542
