to diagnose park safety problems.

159
00:16:39,542 --> 00:16:40,918
It's mine.

160
00:16:43,254 --> 00:16:46,924
<i>So if there's nothing else, we're done.</i>

161
00:17:21,167 --> 00:17:24,128
Oh, fuck. Okay.

162
00:17:25,171 --> 00:17:26,464
Yeah.

163
00:17:26,923 --> 00:17:29,133
Fuck. Come on. Come on.

164
