I want to see it.

167
00:17:41,938 --> 00:17:43,189
Upstairs?

168
00:17:45,066 --> 00:17:46,108
No.

169
00:17:46,984 --> 00:17:48,027
No.

170
00:18:27,525 --> 00:18:29,235
This is so stupid.

171
00:20:09,377 --> 00:20:12,046
You son of a bitch!
I'll put a bullet in your head.

172
