178
00:21:10,020 --> 00:21:13,983
<i>Welcome to Westworld.
Live without limits.</i>

179
00:21:25,035 --> 00:21:26,495
Maeve?

180
00:22:15,669 --> 00:22:17,505
All right, let's get you back.

181
00:22:17,755 --> 00:22:19,590
