188
00:22:35,940 --> 00:22:39,443
<i>You wouldn't remember, because that
life and those memories were erased.</i>

189
00:22:39,610 --> 00:22:41,946
I have been at the
Mariposa for 10 years.

190
00:22:42,947 --> 00:22:45,032
- Before that, I was in New Orleans--
<i>- No.</i>

191
00:22:45,616 --> 00:22:49,453
You've only been the madam at
the Mariposa for the last year or so.

192
00:22:50,079 --> 00:22:51,789
<i>They don't rewrite you completely.</i>

193
00:22:52,248 --> 00:22:54,792
<i>I mean, they could,
