You're dressing her up now?

198
00:23:14,645 --> 00:23:17,940
Is this becoming like
a fucking <i>hentai</i> thing with you now?

199
00:23:18,107 --> 00:23:21,652
No, I just... I just--

200
00:23:21,819 --> 00:23:24,154
You're fucking obsessed!

201
00:23:25,656 --> 00:23:28,656
You know, I didn't turn you in for your
fuck-up before 'cause we're friends,

202
00:23:28,784 --> 00:23:30,578
but that was obviously a bad call.

203
00:23:31,662 --> 00:23:34,164
I mean, next thing I know,
you're gonna be wearing her dress,

204
00:23:35,249 --> 00:23:36,750
whispering sweet nothings in her ear.

205
00:23:38,836 --> 00:23:41,672
Fuck this. I'm telling QA.

206
