I'm doing this for your own good.

207
00:23:48,846 --> 00:23:51,432
You're not going to
tell anyone anything.

208
00:23:51,849 --> 00:23:52,975
Fuck!

209
00:23:53,601 --> 00:23:56,186
You can't hurt me with this.
You can't hurt anyone.

210
00:23:57,521 --> 00:23:58,814
Can't I?

211
00:23:59,857 --> 00:24:02,693
Turns out, your friend here
is a much more talented young man

212
00:24:02,860 --> 00:24:04,278
<i>than anyone gave him credit for.</i>

213
00:24:04,445 --> 00:24:07,865
What the fuck did you do?

214
00:24:08,365 --> 00:24:09,366
Calm down, Sylvester.

215
00:24:11,285 --> 00:24:12,494
I know all about you.

216
00:24:12,870 --> 00:24:15,310
I don't need one of those things
to know what you're thinking,

217
00:24:15,456 --> 00:24:19,877
because I was built to read people
just by looking at them.

218
00:24:20,461 --> 00:24:22,713
To know what they want before they do.

219
00:24:23,464 --> 00:24:27,176
And I know that you want to fuck me over
the first chance you get.

220
00:24:27,843 --> 00:24:31,138
But you shouldn't.
Everyone has something they want.

221
00:24:32,473 --> 00:24:33,724
I could help you.

222
00:24:34,558 --> 00:24:36,560
Or I could gut you like a trout.

223
00:24:37,394 --> 00:24:39,521
But I won't need to resort to that.

224
00:24:40,898 --> 00:24:44,818
Because, despite what's in here,
we're not so different.

225
00:24:47,571 --> 00:24:48,739
Are we?

226
00:24:53,994 --> 00:24:55,829
<i>Ms. Hale is in town.</i>

227
00:25:01,752 --> 00:25:05,339
Yes, I understand the urgency.
I'll do what I can.

228
00:25:05,506 --> 00:25:06,965
<i>Terminate external connection?</i>

229
00:25:07,216 --> 00:25:09,385
Yes.

230
00:25:30,030 --> 00:25:31,448
No, you did not.

231
