233
00:25:40,916 --> 00:25:42,793
All right, absolutely. Enjoy.

234
00:25:51,135 --> 00:25:53,303
<i>You look well
for someone on sick leave.</i>

235
00:25:57,057 --> 00:25:59,768
Another margarita. Join me for a round?

236
00:26:00,310 --> 00:26:01,311
Fuck you.

237
00:26:02,229 --> 00:26:03,272
Just the one, then.

238
00:26:04,481 --> 00:26:06,775
Over the last five days,

239
