242
00:26:17,453 --> 00:26:19,496
Sorry. A man can only take so much.

243
00:26:20,080 --> 00:26:23,500
Creatively speaking, I'm flaccid now.
I can't get it up.

244
00:26:24,668 --> 00:26:26,003
I'm sure you'll recover.

245
00:26:27,838 --> 00:26:29,339
Do you have any idea

246
00:26:29,506 --> 00:26:32,342
